task.summary: - reworked AST to use llvm-style RTTI - reworked Passes to not rely on virtual inheritance
- added Use class - added Operand and Use iteration for IL Values

- added TblGen - reworked CTFE - added ASTContext - added AST PrettyPrinter and Dumper - added AST Traverse / Transform - replaced Record with RecordDecl - replaced shared_ptr's with raw pointers allocated in BumpPtrAllocator - added NamedDecl, DeclContext
- AST rework - Mixins, Static If, Static Else, improved CTFE - Parse Error Recovery - DiagnosticEngine - Driver improvements - Attribute TblGen

- exponent suffix on numeric literals - make TupleType & FunctionType use trailing objects - lldb synt providers for TupleType, FunctionType - added discardableResult attribute - added DeclarationName - added array types with inferred size
